title: Open Floor Plans, Oversize Rain Shower Heads, Modern Grey Cabinetry
posting_body: ['Ask us about our move-in specials!', 'Enjoy our cozy collection of luxury apartments in Oakland, happily tucked in our little pocket of Temescal.', 'We’re dedicated to bringing you a thoughtful and welcoming sanctuary wrapped in the vibrant surrounds of Temescal.', 'We may be small in numbers (43 total residences), but we’re big in what we bring to the table with our unique floor plan options.', 'That’s our promise, and we want you to hold us to it.', 'Contact us today and schedule a tour to learn more about our wonderful community!', "-Expansive 9' Ceilings", '-Garage Parking Available', '-Wood-Style Plank Flooring', '-On-Site Management', '-Easy Access to Public Parking and Hiking Trails', '-Off', 'Street Parking', '-One Block to Dining, Shopping and Entertainment', '-Spacious Closets', '-Modern Kitchens and Finishes', '-Great Natural Light with Large Floor to Ceiling Windows', '-Stainless-Steel and Energy Efficient Appliance Package', '-Rooftop Deck with Dining Area and Lounge', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
